channel.title: Keldagrim - All good things come to an end
channel.description:
Due to the mass amount of leaking we have decided to release the older client not the new one.
[IMG]http://img1.uploadscreenshot.com/images/orig/7/20619070450-orig.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/3mm57.png[/img]
Not going to name off features, it's an amazing client hope someone puts it to good use I put lots of money into it.
Oh, and if you know who originally started selling the client hit me up with a pm.
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2m5hsbc.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/8S6Ci.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/9UXOg.png[/img] [IMG]http://i39.tinypic.com/tasmxl.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Z190u.png[/img]
